# Next.js & Media Standards

- **SSG First**: Always prefer static rendering. Use `generateStaticParams` for dynamic routes [3, 4].
- **SEO**: Every page must export a `metadata` object with a title and description (120-160 chars) [5].
- **Project Images**:
  - Use `next/image` for all project assets.
  - **Prevention of Cropping**: Always use `object-fit: contain` and a defined `aspect-ratio` (e.g., `aspect-video`) to ensure images are not cut.
  - Set `priority` for images in the Hero section to improve LCP [6].
